[Nouns] apportionment, allotment, consignment, assignment, appointment; appropriation; dispensation, distribution; division, deal; repartition, partition; administration.
dividend, portion, contingent, share, allotment, lot, measure, dose; dole, meed, pittance; quantum, ration; ratio, proportion, quota, modicum, mess, allowance; suerte.
[Verbs] apportion, divide; distribute, administer, dispense; billet, allot, detail, cast, share, mete; portion out, parcel out, dole out; deal, carve.
partition, assign, appropriate, appoint.
come in for one's share (participate) [more].
[Adjectives] apportioning; respective.
[Adverbs] respectively, each to each.
